Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[nhara]] (Radius) izwi rinoreva mutsetse unobatanidza goko re[[denderedza]] nemuganhu we[[denderedzwa]]; [[nhara]] ndiyo inotara panogumira [[denderedzwa]]. Muganhu wedenderedzwa une nhambwe dzakafanana panzvimbo dzose zvichibva pa[[goko]] (centre) redenderedzwa. 

Izwi iri rinoshaniswazve kutsanangudza mutsetse unobatanidza [[goko]] re[[urungano]], neuso hweurungano - uso hweurungano hune nhambwe dzakaenzana panzvimbo dzose kubva pagoko.
